data.description: Beauitful 3 bedroom 2.5 bath country living home right by the school!  Many Electrical updates throughout the home done by seller! New outside lights, garage lights, kitchen lights and outlets throughout the home! Roof was done in 2013, radon system installed in 2016, Hot water tank and sump pump 2015. Sump pump has a backup system. AC 2012 and Flooring in kitchen and living room was done within the past few years! This is a Car lovers dream with the extra lights and epoxy flooring done in the garage! You will not want to miss out on a chance to make this wonderful home yours!
